{"name":"Masked Ablate","size":"large","type":"humanoid","tag":"","alignment":"unaligned","hitDice":"10","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":8,"otherArmorDesc":"17 (natural armor)","speed":"40","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"95 (10d10 + 40)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"18","dexPoints":"8","conPoints":"18","intPoints":"7","wisPoints":"10","chaPoints":"3","blindsight":"30","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"60","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"7","customCr":"7 (2,900 XP)","customProf":3,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The shield guardian can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The shield guardian regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the shield guardian can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the shield guardian can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The shield guardian can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the shield guardian's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the shield guardian's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the shield guardian dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Bound","desc":"The [MON] is magically bound to a crature. As long as the [MON] and its master are on the same plane of existence, the master can telepathically call the [MON] to travel to it, and the [MON] knows the distance and direction to it's master. If the [MON] is within 60 feet of its master, half of any damage they take (rounded up) is transferred to the [MON]."},{"name":"Regeneration","desc":"The [MON] regains 10 hit points at the start of its turn if it has at least 1 hit point."},{"name":"Deafening Aura","desc":"A creature who starts it's turn within 15 ft. of the [MON] must make a DC 15 constitution saving throw or take [1d12] thunder damage and be deafened for a minute (no effect on a success). A creature may repeat the save on the end of their turn to remove the condition."},{"name":"Blood for Blood","desc":"Once per turn, when the [MON] hits with a melee attack, it can spend one hit die to deal [1d12] extra necrotic damage."}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"The guardian makes two attacks using _Vengeful Vigil_."},{"name":"Vengeful Vigil","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK + 1] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 2d6 + 1] and an additional [1d8] thunder damage."},{"name":"Thunderwave","desc":"The [MON] casts _thunderwave_ at 4th level. (DC 15 constitution save, 15 ft. cube, 5d8 thunder damage)"}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[{"name":"Shield","desc":"When a creature makes an attack against the wearer of the [MON]'s amulet, the [MON] grants a +2 bonus to the wearer's AC if the [MON]is within 5 feet of the wearer."},{"name":"Retaliation","desc":"If [MON] is hit with a melle attack within 5 ft., it can use it's reaction to attempt to grapple the attacker with _Vengeful Vigil_. The grapple ends automatically if the [MON] attacks any other creature."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[],"damagetypes":[{"name":"bludgeoning","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"}],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[{"name":"blinded"},{"name":"charmed"},{"name":"deafened"},{"name":"exhaustion"},{"name":"frightened"},{"name":"paralyzed"},{"name":"poisoned"}],"languages":[{"name":"Common","speaks":false},{"name":"Orc","speaks":false},{"name":"Skraal","speaks":true},{"name":"Undercommon","speaks":false}],"understandsBut":"can't speak","shortName":"Ablate","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":2,"damage":[]}